# Setup Info

Install vcpkg

Run the following commands:
- git clone https://github.com/Microsoft/vcpkg.git
- ./vcpkg/bootstrap-vcpkg.sh
- vcpkg install sdl2 sdl2-image sld2-ttf

Install cmake, navigate to project root

Run:
- cmake -S . -B build/ 
- make -C build 
- ./build/IgnisEngine

